task.summary:
Add routes Admin with find `admins` collection data API Endpoint. When you want to fetch data, you just be able make a POST to endpoint with dynamic encrypted parameter ( with bcrypt and the plainText is = '123' ) and get response which is you can fetching it.

The endpoint = "http://localhost:4000/api/v1/admin", example Request 
{
   "req" : "$2b$04$y58NUludsBlBrgbNgQ7AXeDqc7W7F.1XOeetePXWy13Qhp9F25cOS" 
 }

